@startuml ViewPost
actor User
participant PostDetail
participant PostsDB
participant Storage

User -> PostDetail: GET /post/42/
PostDetail -> PostsDB: SELECT post 42
PostsDB --> PostDetail: post data (title, content, image, thumbnail)
PostDetail -> PostsDB: SELECT comments WHERE post_id=42 ORDER BY date_posted DESC
PostsDB --> PostDetail: comment rows
PostDetail --> User: HTML with image URLs and comments
User -> Storage: GET /media/blog_pics/.../image.jpg
Storage --> User: 200 image bytes
@enduml
